General.Name: Zhe Jiang Li Zi Yuan Food Co Ltd
General.Description: Zhe Jiang Li Zi Yuan Food Co.,Ltd. engages in the research, development, production, and sale of dairy products, milk-containing beverages, and other beverages in China. Its products include vegetable protein, compound protein, fruit juice, and cereal beverages under the Liziyuan and Plum Garden brand names. Zhe Jiang Li Zi Yuan Food Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1994 and is based in Jinhua, China.
